peers.json
# `peers.seed.json` is checked in: a small (~140 peer) cold-start
# seed harvested from a long-running daemon. Used by CI (which has
# no persistent peerlist) and by fresh local installs. Lives
# alongside the gitignored `peers.json` that gets written at
# daemon shutdown / SavePeers. CI copies it into place before
# starting the daemon.
